Smart fridge 

1. can tell how fresh food are stored in
Keep records of dates when food items are brought, download data from the Interweb knowledge on how long to keep food fresh 
photogrpah the inside of the fridge when out shopping

2. Connected to mobile devices, reminder when current food are about to go bad 
Possible collect recipes for leftovers

3. Connecting with calendar, interactive fridge where users can speak and connect to your personal computer 
know upcoming events and design your eating plans according to life events
Plan planner for the week, category by the amount of time you spend on cooking the meal 
e.g 30mins easy, 80mins medium, 120mins hard.

4. Analysis habits/taste in food, predict future meal/food choices
